Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hohoo ! Neskutočné !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- To je "Horská hruď" !\N- Shh !
