Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto sme to pomenovali "Projekt Dynamit" !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Výstižné !
